Package: hexfont
Type: Package
Title: Unifont hex font files
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Trevor L", "Davis", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                    email = "trevor.l.davis@gmail.com"),
             person("GNU Unifont authors", role = "cph"))
Description: An R data package with all the hex font files from the GNU Unifont Project (v13.0.06) compressed by gzip.  Provides a convenience function for loading in several of them at the same time as a 'bittermelon' 'bm_font' object.
URL: https://github.com/trevorld/hexfont
BugReports: https://github.com/trevorld/hexfont/issues
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: bittermelon (>= 0.1.0-33)
Remotes: github::trevorld/bittermelon
Suggests: testthat
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
